// spirograph.td — Three overlaid spirographs, hand-computed vertex coordinates
//
// Each spoke is a chain of equal-length segments that rotate by a fixed angle.
// Vertices were generated by iterating `turn + forward` N times starting from
// the center (0.5, 0.4) with heading 0 and accumulating (len*cos h, len*sin h)
// each step. Keeping the turtle code would be cleaner; these pre-computed
// coords exist only because Telidraw no longer exposes turtle verbs.

#coord fractions

